{
  "title": "Warmly Spiced Malaysian Chicken Curry",
  "description": "A rich and earthy Malaysian chicken curry featuring Worcestershire sauce, perfect for a midnight craving, made dairy-free friendly and quickly cooked in a pressure cooker.",
