  "instructions": [
    "Heat the oil in the pressure cooker over medium heat.",
    "Add the onion and cook until it is translucent, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the garlic, curry powder, cumin, turmeric, salt, and pepper, and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add the chicken and cook until it is browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the Worcestershire sauce and stir to combine.",
    "Add the coconut milk and stir to combine.",
    "Close the lid of the pressure cooker and set the valve to sealing.",
    "Pressure cook the curry for 10 minutes, then let the pressure release naturally for 10 minutes.",
    "Open the lid and stir the curry, then serve hot over rice or noodles."
